Only for local sites

1) install for work
sudo apt-get install -y nginx php7.1-cli php7.1-fpm php7.1-common php7.1-mysql php7.1-mcrypt php7.1-bcmath php7.1-mbstring php7.1-xml php7.1-curl php7.1-imap php-pear php7.1-dev php-memcached mc mongodb php-mongodb git
and restart php7.*-fpm

2)setup nginx conf file for server in sites-available

3)symlink: sudo ln -s /etc/nginx/sites-available/databases /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/databases

4)add to /etc/hosts

5)restart nginx

6)sudo chown -R username:www-data storage && chown -R 775 storage